{"word":"Aliens","slug":"aliens","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Aliens</b> Strangers, heathen.<br/> To be treated with justice<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=22&verse=21'>Exo 22:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=23&verse=9'>Exo 23:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=19&verse=34'>Lev 19:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=1&verse=16'>Deu 1:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=10&verse=19'>Deu 10:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=24&verse=14'>Deu 24:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=24&verse=17'>Deu 24:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=27&verse=19'>Deu 27:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=7&verse=6'>Jer 7:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=22&verse=3'>Jer 22:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=22&verse=29'>Eze 22:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=3&verse=5'>Mal 3:5</a><br/> Religious privileges of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=49'>Exo 12:49</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=9&verse=14'>Num 9:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=15&verse=15'>Num 15:15</a><br/> Kindness to Edomites, enjoined<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=23&verse=7'>Deu 23:7</a><br/> Jews authorized to purchase, as slaves<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=25&verse=45'>Lev 25:45</a><br/> And to take usury from<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=15&verse=3'>Deu 15:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=23&verse=20'>Deu 23:20</a><br/> Not permitted to make kings of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?bo